  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/renxiaoyi/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u31609576-29.jpg" class="pil" alt="ren" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/renxiaoyi/">ren</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:历史 学术 文化</span><br />

          <span class="">用维新的眼光看整理和批判旧书，眼界渊博见识精审议论畅快，当时恐怕罕有其匹。清儒埋首故纸，梁任公在历算科技一节浩叹再三，于今仍需努力。成书稍欠剪裁，历算部分有重复。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65545122/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u65545122-1.jpg" class="pil" alt="池北" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/65545122/">池北</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          昨天          在读      </div>

      <br/>


